article.description: — Enoch Cheeks scored 20 points as Robert Morris beat Pittsburgh-Greensburg 84-49 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Cheeks leads Robert Morris over Pittsburgh-Greensburg 84-49
article.linkText: Cheeks leads Robert Morris over Pittsburgh-Greensburg 84-49
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Enoch Cheeks scored 20 points as Robert Morris beat Pittsburgh-Greensburg 84-49 on Wednesday night. Cheeks was 8 of 9 shooting (4 for 5 from distance) for the Colonials (1-1). Josh Corbin scored 12 points, shooting 4 for 8 from beyond the arc, and Jackson Last finished with 10 points. JoJo France had 23 points and six rebounds for the Bobcats (0-1). NEXT UP Robert Morris hosts West Virginia Wesleyan next Wednesday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
